## Error Handling & User Documentation

### Error Documentation

All potential errors must be documented for end users, including:

#### Technical Errors

- Include error codes and descriptions
- Provide troubleshooting steps
- Link to common solutions

### Error Handling in Code

```lua
local function SafelyExecuteFunction(func, ...)
    local success, result = pcall(func, ...)
    if not success then
        -- Log error for debugging
        DEFAULT_CHAT_FRAME:AddMessage("Error: " .. tostring(result))
        return nil
    end
    return result
end
```
